Hong Kong Police Mobile App, developed by the Hong Kong Police Force (HKPF), provides you an instant, on-the-go access to the information of HKPF.

Hong Kong Police Mobile App features a series of functions:
(i) Wanted / Missing Persons;
(ii) Crime Prevention Advice;
(iii) Traffic Matters;
(iv) Notification of Public Meeting / Notification of Public Procession;
(v) Crime Statistics;
(vi) Force Vision, Common Purpose and Values;
(vii) Commissioner’s Operational Priorities;
(viii) Press Release;
(ix) Clarification / Response to Media Enquiry or Report;
(x) Recruitment;
(xi) e-Report Room;
(xii) Nearest Police Station and
(xiii) Contact Us

香港警務處研發的香港警察流動應用程式，讓大家可隨時隨地閱覽香港警務處的資訊。

香港警察流動應用程式載有下列各項信息：

(i) 通緝/失蹤人士；
(ii) 防止罪案建議；
(iii) 交通事項；
(iv) 公眾集會通知／公眾遊行通知；
(v) 罪案統計；
(vi) 警隊抱負、目標及價值觀；
(vii) 警務處處長首要行動項目；
(viii) 新聞公報；
(ix) 澄清／回應傳媒查詢或報道；
(x) 警察招募；
(xi) 電子報案室；
(xii) 就近警署及
(xiii) 聯絡我們
